### Question B (14 Marks) `[KTU University Exam - May 2024, Modified]`

**(a)** Explain the **concept of false overflow** in a linear queue with a suitable diagram. How does a circular queue overcome this limitation? Show the **overflow condition** for a circular queue. **(7 marks)**

