    C3 --> D3[Find Min, Swap, Repeat]
    C4 --> D4[Partition around Pivot, Recurse]
    C5 --> D5[Split Halves, Merge Sorted Subarrays]

    D1 --> E([Sorted Array])
    D2 --> E
    D3 --> E
    D4 --> E
    D5 --> E
```

## 4.2 Bubble Sort Pass Flowchart

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    start([Start]) --> init[i = 0]
    init --> condI{i less than n-1?}
    condI -->|No| done([Sorted])
    condI -->|Yes| swapFlag[swapped = 0]
    swapFlag --> jInit[j = 0]
    jInit --> condJ{j less than n-1-i?}
    condJ -->|No| checkFlag{swapped is 0?}
    checkFlag -->|Yes| done
    checkFlag -->|No| iInc[i = i + 1]
    iInc --> condI
    condJ -->|Yes| cmp{a j greater than a j+1?}
    cmp -->|No| jInc[j = j + 1]
    jInc --> condJ
    cmp -->|Yes| doSwap[Swap a j and a j+1, swapped = 1]
    doSwap --> jInc
```

## 4.3 Quick Sort Partition Architecture (Lomuto Scheme)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    pStart([quickSort low, high]) --> pCheck{low less than high?}
    pCheck -->|No| pReturn([Return])
    pCheck -->|Yes| pCall[pi = partition low, high]
    pCall --> pLeft[quickSort low, pi-1]
    pCall --> pRight[quickSort pi+1, high]
    pLeft --> pReturn
    pRight --> pReturn

    partStart([partition low, high]) --> piv[pivot = a high]
    piv --> iInit[i = low - 1]
    iInit --> loopStart[j = low]
    loopStart --> jLoop{j less than high?}
    jLoop -->|No| place[Swap a i+1 with a high]
    jLoop -->|Yes| check{a j less than or equal pivot?}
    check -->|Yes| incI[i = i + 1, swap a i with a j]
    check -->|No| jNext[j = j + 1]
    incI --> jNext
    jNext --> jLoop
    place --> retPi[Return i + 1]
```

