```
Forward: NULL <-> 10 <-> 20 <-> 30 <-> 40 <-> 50 <-> NULL
Backward: NULL <-> 50 <-> 40 <-> 30 <-> 20 <-> 10 <-> NULL
```

**Mark Distribution (7 marks):**
- Struct definition (1 mark)
- `insertAtEnd` correct logic (2 marks)
- Forward traversal (2 marks)
